\{\phi_{n}\}
f\in L_{p}(\mathbb{T}^{d})
||f*\phi_{n} - f||_{p}\rightarrow 0
\left\|\frac{1}{2\pi^d}\int_{[-\pi,\pi)^{d}}(f(\cdot - t) - f(\cdot))\phi_{n}(t)dt\right\|_{p}\leq\frac{1}{2\pi^d}\int_{[-\pi,\pi)^{d}}||f(\cdot - t) - f\cdot)||_{p}|\phi_{n}(t)|dt
\left\|\frac{1}{2\pi^d}\int_{[-\pi,\pi)^{d}}(f(\cdot - t) - f(\cdot))\phi_{n}(t)dt\right\|_{p}\leq \frac{1}{2\pi^d}\int_{[-\pi,\pi)^{d}}\|(f(\cdot - t) - f(\cdot))\phi_{n}(t)\|_{p}dt,
